### ============================================
### COMPLETE PROFILE TESTS
### ============================================

### Step 1: Signup (get token)
POST http://localhost:3004/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testcomplete@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234"
}


### Step 2: Login (copy token)
POST http://localhost:3004/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "testcomplete@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234"
}

### Step 3: Complete Profile (paste token below)
POST http://localhost:3002/api/users/complete-profile
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOjMsImVtYWlsIjoidGVzdGNvbXBsZXRlQGV4YW1wbGUuY29tIiwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJ1c2VyXzE3NzIzNDY5NDc3NDYiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzIzNDY5NTgsImV4cCI6MTc3Mjk1MTc1OH0.l9GV3GE2pu8q15eNcDrMTdjwa7u0-xWyXPnOUq0rPVo
